com.twitter.sdk.android.core.internal.scribe

Class QueueFileEventStorage

  • Object
    • com.twitter.sdk.android.core.internal.scribe.QueueFileEventStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventsStorage

    public class QueueFileEventStorage
extends Object
implements EventsStorage
    An implementation of EventsStorage backed by a QueueFile. Note that this class is not thread safe and relies on upstream collaborators to ensure thread safe access.
